---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { sitePaths } from '../utils/paths';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="页面未找到"
  description="请求的 PonyLab 页面不存在，可能已经移动或尚未创建。"
  pageClass="not-found-page"
>
  <section class="not-found page-shell">
    <p class="not-found__code">404 / LOST SIGNAL</p>
    <h1>这里暂时没有记录</h1>
    <p>地址可能写错了，或者这份实验记录还没有公开。</p>
    <div class="not-found__actions">
      <a href={sitePaths.page('/')}>返回首页</a>
      <a href={sitePaths.page('/blog/')}>浏览博客</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .not-found {
    display: grid;
    min-height: calc(100svh - var(--site-header-height) - 8rem);
    align-content: center;
    justify-items: start;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    padding-block: clamp(5rem, 14vw, 10rem);
  }

  .not-found__code {
    color: var(--color-accent-warm);
    font: 700 0.78rem var(--font-mono);
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  }

  h1 { font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 8vw, 6rem); }
  .not-found > p:not(.not-found__code) { max-width: 38rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); }
  .not-found__actions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: var(--space-3); margin-top: var(--space-4); }
  .not-found__actions a {
    min-height: 2.75rem;
    padding: 0.7rem 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    background: var(--color-surface);
  }
</style>
